+CASMETA command
+---------------
+
+casmeta <key> <cas>\r\n
+
+Updates only the CAS metadata for an existing item. The stored value, flags,
+and expiration time are preserved.
+
+Response:
+  UPDATED\r\n
+
+If the item does not exist, CASMETA returns:
+  NOT_FOUND\r\n
